(secondQuint)A Fixed Triple Combination Cream for Solar Lentigines Associated to Cryotherapy.

 To evaluate safety and efficacy of Tri-Luma(R) cream as an adjunctive treatment to cryotherapy when used in the pre- and post-procedure phases for the treatment of solar lentigines on the back of the hands and in the prevention of post-inflammatory hyperpigmentation after cryotherapy.

 The study has 13 weeks for each subject.

 Five visits will take place: at Baseline, week 2, 5, 9 and 13 after the cryotherapy.

